a) Go to “My Orders page” and press the orange button “New order”;  b) Choose the type of the request – New order;

c) Select the initial entries:
 Data of dispatch, Route, Container type, Container ownership;    
d) Choose the Rate, for selecting the rate press “Select offer”; you can filter the price rates by the Destination, Customs clearance location or Currency; then press “Select offer”

Use this feature if you want to make a new request using the previously entered info.  а) Go to “My orders”;  б) Find a previous request and press “Repeat”;

в) Fill in the fields; fields marked with * are mandatory; and press “Create”.
After sending the request you will get a notification with all the request details on your email.  You can continue the correspondence by sending a REPLY to the message.

— Go to “Add new legal entity” subsection;  
— Enter INN of the legal entity;  
— Press “Find”. If there are a few companies with the same INN in the system, you will get a service notification. After this enter registration reason code (KPP) and press “find”.
 After completing the form successfully, the company will be added to your list as temporary, and you will be able to send an access request for any on the companies of FESCO Group.

To download the documents in archive file:
a) Go to the documents list in Electronic archive menu;  b) Tick the documents needed;  c) Press “Download archive”; 
  d) Wait until the download status changes from “In process” to “Done” and press “Open”;    e) Press “Download”; 
  The archive file will be downloaded to your computer.
